    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1127336530">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1127336530" class="vote-count">7</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1127336530" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1127336530">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuyan545/">亚比煞</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">红楼梦写的是青春，是桃花源，金瓶梅写的是成人，是大染缸。红楼女儿各有各的美好，金瓶中的女人却各有各的不堪。红楼是情而不淫，金瓶是淫而无情。红楼是理想，金瓶是现实。红楼读毕是伤感如临大雪，金瓶读完是冷酷如对深渊。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

